      "# Gene Expression Analysis",
      "",
      "Gene expression, 中文基因表达, measures how DNA information becomes RNA and functional products.",
      "",
      "## Statistics",
      "",
      "差异表达统计 compares conditions while controlling library size and multiple testing. ",
      "",
      "## Aliases",
      "",
      "Expression level, transcript abundance, and 转录水平 describe related but not identical measurements.",
      "",
      "## Limits",
      "",
      "Batch effects can dominate biological signal when experimental design is unbalanced."
